'''無限塔'''（{{lang-en|Tower Infinity}}）座落於[[南韓|南韓]][[首爾|首爾]][[仁川國際機場|仁川國際機場]]附近，高453公尺，為世界首座具備隱形功能的摩天大樓。<ref name=archi>{{cite web|last=Chan|first=Kelly|title=GDS Architects to Design World's First Invisible Tower|url=http://www.architizer.com/blog/invisible-tower-gds/|publisher=Architizer|accessdate=2013-09-16 |archive-date=2017-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170906035927/https://architizer.com/blog/invisible-tower-gds/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=cnn>{{cite news|last=Cripps|first=Karla|title=Coming soon: World's first 'invisible' tower|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2013/09/12/travel/seoul-invisible-skyscraper-tower-infinity/?hpt=travel_hp_herobox|accessdate=16 September 2013|newspaper=CNN|date=16 September 2013|archive-date=2017-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170409200604/http://edition.cnn.com/2013/09/12/travel/seoul-invisible-skyscraper-tower-infinity/?hpt=travel_hp_herobox|dead-url=no}}</ref>頂樓有觀景台，建築公司表示，未來內部將有雲霄飛車、水上樂園、音樂噴泉、景觀花園、婚禮會場、美食餐廳等娛樂用途。

无限塔将利用[[LED|LED]]照明和[[光學|光學]][[攝影|攝影]]技術再加上電腦操作，營造大樓隱形效果。在特地時間和特地角度，玻璃帷幕會把大樓遮住，並反射其他影像，在視覺上產生錯覺，使其透明。<ref name=cnn /><ref name=insider>{{cite news|last=Willett|first=Megan|title=Korea Will Soon Be Home To The World's First 'Invisible' Skyscraper|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/tower-infinity-first-invisible-skyscraper-2013-9|accessdate=16 September 2013|newspaper=Business Insider|date=11 September 2013|archive-date=2017-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171222131720/http://www.businessinsider.com/tower-infinity-first-invisible-skyscraper-2013-9|dead-url=no}}</ref>

